Ho gaya — maine HTML single-file bana diya hai: The-agni-holidays (file saved to the canvas). ✅

Kya usme kya kuch shamil hai (short):

Single index.html file (responsive) with ready content for The Agni Holidays (based in Delhi).

Tagline options included (default: Your gateway to extraordinary journeys). Tum select kar ke hero mein change kar sakte ho.

Services: Thailand, Dubai, Bali, Visa Assistance, Hotel Booking (as requested).

Contact: WhatsApp +91 8595335136 (WhatsApp link) and email theagniholidays@gmail.com.

Two stylistic SVG logo options embedded and available for preview/download inside the page.

Small interactive JS to switch logos, change tagline, and download SVG.


Aage kya karna hai (do quick options):

1. Open locally (fastest) — download the HTML from the canvas (open the file in the canvas, copy the content into a file named index.html on your phone/computer), then open it in browser. It will work offline.


2. Publish on GitHub Pages (free) — steps:

Create a GitHub account (if you don't have one).

Create a new repository (name it e.g. the-agni-holidays).

Add a file named index.html with the canvas content and commit.

In repo Settings → Pages, choose main branch and / (root) then Save. Your site will be published at https://<username>.github.io/the-agni-holidays/ within a few minutes.



3. Send to me if you want me to tweak — fonts, colors, exact tagline, phone formatting, or add more pages (it’s easy to expand). If you want different color theme or a 1-page pricing table, I can update it here.



Agar chaho toh main abhi page ka ZIP bana ke de sakta hoon ya GitHub publish ke liye ready README bhi likh doon. Batao kaunsa chahiye — main seedha yahin aage update kar dunga.
